users.about: I'm a "geek girl" fell in love with cultural anthropology, a web application developer who went to divinity school to study social justice theology, an individual living with AD/HD and depression who refuses to live in the (mental health) closet. I am an open source evangelist and a usability advocate. I believe accessible technology is a human right.
